-expression-language","i-lucide-file-code",{"title":182,"path":183,"stem":184,"icon":185},"CRI Format","\u002Freference\u002Fcri-format","3.reference\u002F4.cri-format","i-lucide-link",{"title":187,"path":188,"stem":189,"icon":190},"SDK Packages","\u002Freference\u002Fsdk-packages","3.reference\u002F5.sdk-packages","i-lucide-package",{"id":192,"title":11,"body":193,"description":397,"extension":398,"links":399,"meta":400,"navigation":401,"path":12,"seo":402,"stem":13,"__hash__":403},"docs\u002F1.apps\u002F1.introduction.md",{"type":194,"value":195,"toc":389},"minimark",[196,200,205,208,212,239,243,324,330,336,342,346,349,382],[197,198,199],"p",{},"Kinotic is a next-generation cloud operating system that abstracts away infrastructure complexity so developers and AI agents can focus on what matters: building great applications.",[201,202,204],"h2",{"id":203},"vibe-coding-at-scale","Vibe Coding at Scale",[197,206,207],{},"The rise of AI-assisted development has unlocked a new paradigm -- rapid iteration driven by natural-language intent and intelligent code generation. Kinotic is purpose-built for this paradigm. Whether a human developer or an AI agent is writing the code, Kinotic provides the guardrails, services, and runtime that turn quick prototypes into production-grade systems.",[201,209,211],{"id":210},"core-components","Core Components",[213,214,215,222,227,233],"ul",{},[216,217,218,221],"li",{},[219,220,5],"strong",{}," -- Applications that run on Kinotic OS. Today, Kinotic Apps are built with TypeScript running on Bun -- you write standard TypeScript for domain models, business logic, and UI, and the platform handles infrastructure, deployment, and scaling. Support for Go, Java, and Python backends is coming soon.",[216,223,224,226],{},[219,225,128],{}," -- The cloud operating system that runs your apps. It provides authentication, authorization, persistence, service mesh, observability, and deployment infrastructure out of the box.",[216,228,229,232],{},[219,230,231],{},"Kinotic OS Cloud"," -- A fully managed SaaS offering of Kinotic OS. No servers to provision, no infrastructure to maintain.",[216,234,235,238],{},[219,236,237],{},"Kinotic CLI"," -- The developer tool that ties it all together. Use it to initialize projects, define entities, generate service code, and deploy applications.",[201,240,242],{"id":241},"why-kinotic","Why Kinotic?",[244,245,246,262],"table",{},[247,248,249],"thead",{},[250,251,252,256,259],"tr",{},[253,254,255],"th",{},"Concern",[253,257,258],{},"Without Kinotic",[253,260,261],{},"With Kinotic",[263,264,265,277,292,303,314],"tbody",{},[250,266,267,271,274],{},[268,269,270],"td",{},"Authentication & Authorization",[268,272,273],{},"Wire up OIDC, RBAC, and session management yourself",[268,275,276],{},"Built in -- configure once, enforce everywhere",[250,278,279,281,284],{},[268,280,59],{},[268,282,283],{},"Choose a database, write migrations, build CRUD endpoints",[268,285,286,287,291],{},"Define entities, run ",[288,289,290],"code",{},"kinotic sync",", get a full service layer",[250,293,294,297,300],{},[268,295,296],{},"Service Mesh",[268,298,299],{},"Deploy sidecars, configure routing, handle retries",[268,301,302],{},"Automatic service discovery and RPC across the application",[250,304,305,308,311],{},[268,306,307],{},"CI\u002FCD",[268,309,310],{},"Maintain pipelines, container registries, rollout strategies",[268,312,313],{},"Handled by the platform",[250,315,316,318,321],{},[268,317,152],{},[268,319,320],{},"Instrument code, deploy collectors, build dashboards",[268,322,323],{},"SBOM generation, metrics, and tracing are included",[197,325,326,329],{},[219,327,328],{},"Rapid prototyping."," Go from an idea to a running application in minutes with the CLI and generated services.",[197,331,332,335],{},[219,333,334],{},"Enterprise-ready."," Role-based access control, software bill of materials, and full observability mean you never have to rewrite for production.",[197,337,338,341],{},[219,339,340],{},"Internet scale."," The platform is designed to scale horizontally from day one.",[201,343,345],{"id":344},"what-these-docs-cover","What These Docs Cover",[197,347,348],{},"This documentation walks through everything you need to build and ship a Kinotic App:",[350,351,352,357,362,367,372,377],"ol",{},[216,353,354,356],{},[219,355,15],{}," -- Scaffold a project and persist your first entity in under five minutes.",[216,358,359,361],{},[219,360,19],{}," -- Understand how organizations, applications, projects, and artifacts fit together.",[216,363,364,366],{},[219,365,38],{}," -- Publish and consume services across your application.",[216,368,369,371],{},[219,370,59],{}," -- Define entities, configure indexes, and run queries.",[216,373,374,376],{},[219,375,92],{}," -- Set up authentication and authorization.",[216,378,379,381],{},[219,380,107],{}," -- Ship your application to Kinotic OS or Kinotic OS Cloud.",[197,383,384,385,388],{},"Ready to build something? Head to the ",[386,387,15],"a",{"href":16}," to create your first Kinotic App.",{"title":390,"searchDepth":391,"depth":391,"links":392},"",2,[393,394,395,396],{"id":203,"depth":391,"text":204},{"id":210,"depth":391,"text":211},{"id":241,"depth":391,"text":242},{"id":344,"depth":391,"text":345},"Learn what Kinotic is, why it exists, and how it helps developers and AI agents build enterprise-grade applications at scale.","md",null,{},true,{"title":11,"description":397},"KS8lMhwmX0TK0R1hyWFjw7QQuC5ScVq_7LfRQyqnkg4",[399,405],{"title":15,"path":16,"stem":17,"description":406,"children":-1},"Get started building your first Kinotic App -- from installation to a running CRUD service in under five minutes.",1776071038433]